        {
            "title": "港元1個月拆息三連升  至逾3.3厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15211606&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息上升，與樓按相關的1個月拆息報3.30649厘，升7.339基點，連升3日，是5月6日後最高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240621_po_bankrupt01_source-bp_fb.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240621_po_bankrupt01_source-bp_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">H按息率現在為H+1.3厘，為4.6065，但封頂息為5.25(P)-1.75厘，即3.5厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以樓價600萬元，按揭70%即貸款420萬元，年期30年計算，若息率4.6065厘，每月還款21547元，但由於封頂3.5厘，每月還款額18860元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映銀行資金成本的三個月拆息報3.3072厘，升3.41基點，是5月7日後最高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">　　隔夜息報3.98226厘，升85.869基點，是5月2日後最高；一周拆息升54.119基點，報3.70548厘，兩周則升48.131基點，報3.64774厘。長息方面，六個月拆息升3.488基點，報3.26524厘，一年期則升6.97基點，報3.30363厘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15211606-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%831%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e4%b8%89%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87-%e8%87%b3%e9%80%be3-3%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/bplib_20230707-125253_20230707_FI_source-licensed_HKD_shutterstock_fb_1_source-licensed_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 09:00:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "傳投資者1.2億購入新世界永康街基座商場  呎價1.38萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15209196&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市傳新世界發展(00017)旗下長沙灣甲廈「83永康街」基座商場，最近獲投資者約1.2億元購入作長線投資，以商場建築面積約8,660平方呎成交計算，平均成交呎價逾1.38萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據代理透露，長沙灣新落成的甲廈「83永康街」，設有6間舖位的基座商場，舖位建築面積介乎750至2,000平方呎。最近有本地投資者斥資約1.2億元大手掃入整個基座商場作長線收租用途，計劃出租給零售及餐廳等商戶。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據政府差餉物業估價署數據，2025年第二季零售商業物業投資成交宗數按季上升約33%，上半年成交宗數相比2024年同比增長近15%，涉及近60億港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場已趨穩定，跌幅收窄，不少投資者開始重新審視高質量、具穩定回報的物業投資機遇，其中「83永康街」項目因其甲級寫字樓定位及核心區域優勢，備受投資者青睞。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15209196-15209196",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/PP_00017_-Wing-Hong-Street_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 09:00:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息全線上升　1個月拆息升穿3厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15208525&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息連續兩日全線上升，普遍升至3厘以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">與樓按相關的1個月拆息升至3.23厘，上升近42基點。以按揭息率H+1.3計算，現按揭利率為4.53厘，封頂利率為P-1.75%，約為3.5厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映銀行資金成本的3個月拆息升至3.27厘，升約36個基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於隔夜拆息升約39個基點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15208525-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%87%e3%80%801%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf3%e5%8e%98-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 09:00:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "和鉑醫藥折讓9.45%配股   集資逾5億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">和鉑醫藥(02142)宣布以每股11.50元的價格配股，較上日收市價12.7元折讓9.45%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/776x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250829_FI_02142_WEB.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/776x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250829_FI_02142_WEB.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售股份數量4502.2萬股，佔現股本5.45%，及擴大後股本5.17%。集資總額及淨額分別為5.18億元及5.12億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售所得款項淨額約50%用於開拓創新藥物資產的研發；約40%用於推進現有管線藥物資產的臨床試驗；及約10%將用於營運資金及其他一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214308-%e5%92%8c%e9%89%91%e9%86%ab%e8%97%a5%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%939-45%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e9%80%be5%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/02142-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 09:00:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "晶泰控股折讓7.12%配股籌26.53億元 預期未來5至10年用於業務發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶泰控股(02228)公布，今早與配售代理訂立協議，擬配股集資約26.53億元；配股價9.28元，較該股昨收市10.06元折讓7.75%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"晶泰科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/02228-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"晶泰科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/02228-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">晶泰科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價10.098元比較，配股價較之折讓8.1%，較前30個交易日平均收市價7.52元則有溢價23.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今次已是該公司過去12個月以來第3次配股，之前兩次是在今年1月及2月，這兩次配股所得款項至今尚未完全動用。其中1月配股集資淨額11.25億元，截至6月底時已動用6.54億元，餘下估計在2027年底前動用；2月配股集資淨額20.8億元，截至6月底時已動用5.08億元，餘額估計在2034年底前動用。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於今次配股淨額約26.3億元，同樣擬用於產品持續迭代升級、產品商業化及業務發展、潛在收購及投資等多方面，目前預期於未來5至10年內將今次集資所得用作上述擬定用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214301-%e6%99%b6%e6%b3%b0%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%937-12%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c26-53%e5%84%84%e5%85%83-%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f%e6%9c%aa%e4%be%865%e8%87%b310%e5%b9%b4%e7%94%a8%e6%96%bc%e6%a5%ad",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250603_CR_Bay-area-visit2_source-bp_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 09:00:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "微創機器人半年經調整虧損收窄55.5% 研發成本降46%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">微創機器人(02252)公布，上半年若非香港財務報告準則的經調整淨虧損9710.8萬元(人民幣．下同)，按年收窄55.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：微創機器人2024年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250528_FI_source-web_02252-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：微創機器人2024年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250528_FI_source-web_02252-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：微創機器人2024年度年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若按香港財報準則，上半年公司權益股東應佔虧損1.13億元，也較去年減少59.1%。收入1.76億元，按年增加77%；毛利7150.6萬元，增長52.1%，主要得益於圖邁的海外銷售高速增長，毛利率41%則較去年同期減少6個百分點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內自由現金流淨流出1.35億元，較去年同期減少42.8%，主要得益於淨虧損收窄以及固定資產投資已階段性完成。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214279-%e5%be%ae%e5%89%b5%e6%a9%9f%e5%99%a8%e4%ba%ba%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%8455-5-%e7%a0%94%e7%99%bc%e6%88%90%e6%9c%ac%e9%99%8d46",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/02252.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 08:45:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "海天味業半年純利升13.3% 中期息每股0.26元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海天味業(03288)公布，上半年歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤39.1億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升13.3%；擬派中期息每股0.26元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：海天味業招股書</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">實內實現營業收入152.3億元，按年升7.6%；其中調味品業務收入145.6億元，較去年同期更增長10.4%。毛利59.8億元，按年升17.1%；毛利率39.3%，按年提升3.2個百分點，主要由於部分原材料市場價格下降，以及生產環節效率提升。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上半年度海天味業從經營活動所得現金為15.05億元，按年增加33.6%。截至6月底時現金及銀行存款299.99億元，較去年底增加35.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214259-%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%a9%e5%91%b3%e6%a5%ad%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%8713-3-%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a10-26%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250619_FI_source-web_03288.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 08:35:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "波司登：媒體報道公司或收購Canada Goose的內容不實",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">繼安踏(02020)之後，波司登(03998)今早亦發公告就可能收購Canada Goose的報道澄清，表明有關報道內容不實。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：Canada Goose官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508029_FI_source-web_CG.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：Canada Goose官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508029_FI_source-web_CG.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：Canada Goose官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">之前市場傳出，加拿大高檔羽絨品牌Canada Goose的大股東貝恩資本，有意出售所持部份或全部股權，外電指已獲博裕及安宏資本對Canada Goose私有化的口頭報價，對應估值約13.5美元，其他潛在買家包括安踏、波司登及方源資本組成的財團。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安踏昨天已發公告澄清，並非該潛在收購的一方。波司登今早發出的公告亦指有關報道內容不實，公司無任何應披露而未披露的信息。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214235-%e6%b3%a2%e5%8f%b8%e7%99%bb%ef%bc%9a%e5%aa%92%e9%ab%94%e5%a0%b1%e9%81%93%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e6%88%96%e6%94%b6%e8%b3%bccanada-goose%e7%9a%84%e5%85%a7%e5%ae%b9%e4%b8%8d%e5%af%a6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231127_FI_source-web_03998bosiden_fgb.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 08:25:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期夜期均收復二萬五 高水逾百點 重磅港股ADR齊反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時15分升141點或0.56%，報25154點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報25121點，較香港上日現貨收市高122點或0.49%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣599.4元，較上日香港收市高5.44元或0.92%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣116.5元，較上日香港收市高0.71元或0.61%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣103.4元，較上日香港收市高1.66元或1.63%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣118.4元，較上日香港收市高3.24元或2.82%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣53.5元，較上日香港收市高0.39元或0.73%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240916_FI_source-web_03690-704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240916_FI_source-web_03690-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣101.1元，較上日香港收市高0.45元或0.45%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣73元，較上日香港收市高0.52元或0.72%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣452.6元，較上日香港收市高2.78元或0.62%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣56.4元，較上日香港收市高0.2元或0.35%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣7.5元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">9月份恒指夜市期指收報25104點，升198點，較上日恒指收市24998點，高水105點。9月份科指期貨夜市收報5719點，較上日科指收市高水75點；9月份國指期貨夜市收報8965點，較上日國指收市高水48點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15214250-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e5%9d%87%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94-%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be%e7%99%be%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e9%bd%8a%e5%8f%8d",
